comments: Kuzma (WAS) slides his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Kuzma (WAS) jumps alongside Rozier's (MIA) path and marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Martin (MIA) moves alongside Kuzma's (WAS) path and absorbs the marginal body contact during Kuzma's drive in transition.
Rozier (MIA) moves slightly forward with his forearm resting against Jones' (WAS) side, as marginal body contact occurs with Jones during his driving shot attempt.
Kuzma (WAS) turns and delivers contact into Butler's (MIA) body affecting Butler's driving shot attempt.
Avdija (WAS) briefly grasps Rozier's (MIA) arm off-ball and marginal contact occurs as Avdija releases away to retrieve the inbound pass.
Avdija (WAS) and Rozier (MIA) briefly engage and disengage with one another in transition.
Adebayo (MIA) engages and disengages with Kuzma (WAS) as marginal contact occurs prior to the pick.
Robinson (MIA) immediately slides his hand off of Kuzma's (WAS) side and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
Butler (MIA) grasps Avdija's (WAS) jersey and immediately releases it as marginal contact occurs in pursuit of the rebound.
Kuzma (WAS) and Adebayo (MIA) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Kuzma (WAS) lightly brushes Adebayo's (MIA) left arm and marginal contact occurs during his shot attempt in the lane.
Kispert (WAS) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Martin's (MIA) arm after the release.
Butler (MIA) collides with Martin (MIA) and makes incidental contact with Kuzma's (WAS) body as he falls to the floor after the made shot attempt.
Rozier (MIA) and Kuzma (WAS) engage and disengage with one another and marginal contact occurs off-ball.
On the spin move, Kuzma (WAS) makes contact with Rozier's (MIA) head.
Robinson (MIA) briefly grasps Coulibaly's (WAS) arm and immediately slides his hand off as Coulibaly defends under the pick.
Adebayo (MIA) and Kispert (WAS) come together off-ball and absorb each other's contact.
Robinson (MIA) gathers the pass on his right foot and legally steps into his shot attempt.
